  <h3 id="image">Adding image</h3>
  <p>Images added to a card will be displayed above the heading and text. The image is set as a decorative image by default, with the alternative text being null.</p>
  <p>Only use cards with images if you have evidence that they help your users, for example, where you can show that they motivate users.</p>
  
